[{"id":"54315ed634e74697e39b5023c0bd3711","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: Meeting with Nathan Myhrvold","date":"2008-04-14T00:54:48.000Z","formatted_date":"Apr 14, 2008","formatted_time":"12:54 AM","body":" \n \n \n \n \n \n \nLesley Groff\nExecutive Assistant to Jeffrey Epstein\n \n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Lori Hargrave [mailto:lorih@intven.com] \nSent: Friday, April 11, 2008 4:56 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: RE: Meeting with Nathan Myhrvold\n\n\n\nLesley,\n\n \n\nDo you know if Jeffrey is able to meet with Nathan next week?\n\nThanks!\n\n \n\nBest,\n\nLori\n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Lori Hargrave \nSent: Tuesday, April 08, 2008 2:11 PM\nTo: 'Lesley Groff'\nSubject: Meeting with Nathan Myhrvold\n\n \n\nHi Lesley,\n\n \n\nNathan is going to be in NYC once again next week (4/14 - 4/18), and he\nasked me to inquire whether or not Jeffrey is available for a meeting\nwith him.  Please let me know whether or not this is a possibility and,\nif so, what days/times look best for Jeffrey's calendar.  \n\n \n\nThanks very much!\n\n \n\nKind regards,\n\nLori\n\n \n\nLori Hargrave\n\nIntellectual Ventures\n\n \n\nhttp://www.intellectualventures.com\n\nlorih@intven.com <mailto:lorih@intven.com> \n\nOffice: 425.283.4781\n\nFax: 425.679-0589\n\n \n\nThis message may contain confidential and/or legally privileged\ninformation. If you are not the intended recipient of the message,\nplease destroy it. Any unauthorized dissemination, distribution or\ncopying of the material in this message, and any attachments to the\nmessage, is strictly forbidden.  (c) 2008 all rights reserved\n\n \n\n","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\">\n<HTML xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\" xmlns:v = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o = \n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office